                        </div>
                        <h3 class="highlight-title">Building Dreams Since 2016</h3>
                        <div class="highlight-stats">
                            <div class="stat-circle">
                                <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Dreams Built</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-circle">
                                <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Years of Magic</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="highlight-features">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <div class="feature-icon">üèóÔ∏è</div>
                                <span>Licensed & Insured</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <div class="feature-icon">‚≠ê</div>
                                <span>5-Star Rated</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <div class="feature-icon">üöÄ</div>
                                <span>Fast Delivery</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="highlight-cta">
                            <a href="/contact" class="highlight-btn">Start Your Dream Project</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder Bio Section -->
    <section class="founder-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="founder-content">
                <div class="founder-image founder-image-desktop">
                    <img src="/AboutPage/Founder.jpg" alt="Founder of Wolf Construction Ltd" class="founder-photo">
                </div>
                <div class="founder-text">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <span class="section-badge">Leadership</span>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Meet Our Founder</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="founder-image founder-image-mobile">
                        <img src="/AboutPage/Founder.jpg" alt="Founder of Wolf Construction Ltd" class="founder-photo">
                    </div>
                    <p class="founder-bio">
                        Our founder, [Founder's Name], started in the building trade with a passion for turning ideas into solid, lasting structures. With over 20 years of hands-on experience and Licensed Building Practitioner (LBP) certification, he has led Wolf Construction Ltd from its first small renovation to large-scale new builds and design + build solutions.
                    </p>
                    <p class="founder-philosophy">
                        His belief is that construction is not just about bricks and timber‚Äîit's about building trust, relationships, and communities.
                    </p>
                    <div class="founder-credentials">
                        <div class="credential">
                            <div class="credential-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span>Licensed Building Practitioner (LBP)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="credential">
                            <div class="credential-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span>20+ Years Experience</span>
